PSG have reportedly slashed their asking price for Neymar as they look to do a deal with Barcelona. PSG previously wanted a deal in excess of £270m (€300m), but are now ready to take much less. French publication Le Parisien claim PSG want between 130 and 150 million euros and two players thrown into the mix. Neymar is keen to return to Spain after failing to get to grips with life in Paris. JUST IN: 'Neymar wants Barcelona return' PSG rule out Mbappe transfer PSG plotting move for Manchester United''s Paul Pogba Dear Esteemed reader, As part of our drive to keep improving the content of our newspaper, we are conducting a readership survey to enable us serve you better. Kindly take two minutes of your time to fill in this questionnaire. Thank you for your time. Click here to begin